  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When this adversaries ally would take damage from a hostile creature, this adversary gains a rank Cursed Love. When they would see an ally reduced to 0 hit points and killed, they gain 10 ranks of Cursed Love. When this creature would gain 10 ranks of Cursed Love, they spend all accumulated ranks and enter a berserkers rage, fueled by Love. While in this rage, attacks they make are all at advantage and ignores penalties. This Rage lasts until the end of their next turn.</p>",
